author: 滇西小哥 Dianxi Xiaoge
description:
※Click "cc" on the lower right menu to choose your subtitle language.

This episode gathers all the “water-grown delicacies” from past videos into one collection.
Freshwater fish from the rivers, shrimp from the lakes, tiny mountain crabs, all kinds of shellfish, and even the little treasures found in village streams…
Just clean them well, prepare a few simple ingredients, and cook them in the most straightforward way — that’s how you bring out the freshest flavor.

Hello, everyone! I am Dianxi Xiaoge, a Yunnan native. If you enjoy my videos, please keep subscribing to my channel. I'll continue to share my life and Yunnan-styled food in my uploads. Wish you have a happy life and enjoy tasty food every day
